                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18200217-152-off880 t18200217-152-cd881"></join>, having in his custody and possession a bill of exchange for payment of 50 l. - (setting it forth, drawn by 
                     <persName id="t18200217-152-person1459">
                        Thomas 
                        Welldon
                     <interp inst="t18200217-152-person1459" type="surname" value="Welldon"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18200217-152-person1459" type="given" value="Thomas"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18200217-152-person1459" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
