                  , at two months after date, on Mr. Samuel Welldon, Cambridge) - on the same day feloniously did forge and counterfeit on the said bill, an acceptance thereof, with intent to defraud 
                     
                        <persName id="t18200217-152-victim1461" type="victimName">
                           Samuel 
                           Welldon
                        <interp inst="t18200217-152-victim1461" type="surname" value="Welldon"></interp>
