                        <interp inst="t18200217-152-victim1461" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     </persName>
                     
                  
               
                  </rs>.</p>
               <p>SECOND COUNT, for feloniously uttering the said forged acceptance as true, with the like intent.</p>
               <p>TWO OTHER COUNTS, the same, only stating his intent to be to defraud 
               
                  <persName id="t18200217-152-victim1463" type="victimName">
                     Joseph 
                     Parkin
                  <interp inst="t18200217-152-victim1463" type="surname" value="Parkin"></interp>
