                  </persName>
            . I am clerk to Mr. Price, the attorney for the prosecution. I know the hand-writing of Mr. 
               <persName id="t18200217-152-person1467">
                  Samuel 
                  Welldon
               <interp inst="t18200217-152-person1467" type="surname" value="Welldon"></interp>
