             of Cambridge. I do not know whether the writing is his or not. I am not well acquainted with it.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. My brother gave it to me. I wrote to him not to honour the bill, because Parkin only advanced me 15 l. on it. He keeps a noted house for thieves. My brother Samuel is ill, and not able to attend.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18200217-152-person1471">
